_WEBTRIT_ANDROID_RELEASE_UPLOAD_KEYSTORE: Optional path to directory containing upload-keystore-metadata.json and keystore file. Used to configure Android release signing automatically. If not provided, fallback to key.properties will be used.
_WEBTRIT_HTTP_ALLOWED_DOMAINS_DESCRIPTIO: List of HTTP domains allowed for cleartext (non-HTTPS) traffic. Use format: 'domain,includeSubdomains' (optional), separated by semicolons. Example: '127.0.0.1,false;dev.api.com,true;local.test'. If 'includeSubdomains' is omitted, it defaults to false. '127.0.0.1' is required for just_audio to enable local proxy features like headers and caching.
